title: 4/10/16- GH Fantasy Weekend 3- New Jersey Super Event
desc: Join us for our GH Fantasy Weekend #3 on Sunday, April 10, 2016 The GH Fantasy Weekend will be hosted by Tyler Christopher & Laura Wright, both fan favorites from ABC's General Hospital.? The event will also feature Vinnessa Antoine, Robert Palmer Watkins, Ryan Carnes, Will DeVry, Finola Hughes, Ryan Paevey, Rebecca Budig, Brandon Barash & Kirsten Storms from GH- you'll get to see all of them for a star studded afternoon in NJ! Come spend the day with your GH favorites! $310 plus tax and ticket fees - includes a 90 minute meet/greet with the actors for autographs and photo ops plus the two hour show, limited to 100 tickets. Limit of 3 autographs per celebrity.? $107 tickets plus tax and ticket fees- two hour show featuring Q & A, interviews, and fan fun.? Bring your cameras but no videotaping allowed.?
